# Frontend Redesign: Sajtmaskin

## Design Principles
- **Super minimalist** — as few words as possible everywhere
- **Apple + Google + ChatGPT** aesthetic: clean, generous whitespace, calm
- **Proactive UX** — OpenClaw asks the user, not the other way around
- **Progressive disclosure** — options behind elegant tabs/dropdowns, never visible by default

## Color Palette
- **Background:** Deep navy (~#1a1f36, HSL ~222 40% 15%)
- **Primary/CTA:** Orange (~#ff6b35, HSL ~14 90% 60%)
- **Foreground:** White / near-white
- **No teal** — remove current accent color from UI
- **Ring/focus:** Orange to match primary

## Navigation Pattern (ALL pages)
- Hamburger menu top-right (ALL breakpoints, not just mobile)
- Login: icon-only (User/LogIn icon), never text
- "Kom igång gratis": subtle outline button (guest only)
- All nav links live INSIDE the hamburger menu
- Unify landing-v2/navbar and layout/navbar into one shared pattern

## Typography
- Reduce to 2 fonts max (Geist Sans body + Space Grotesk headings)
- Remove unused Inter font
- Generous line-height, minimal font weights

## Component Rules
- Buttons: calm, no 3D/glow effects
- Dialogs: softer overlays, tighter spacing
- Empty states: one short line + single CTA
- Loading: minimal spinner, no marketing narrative

## Analysis Files (detailed per-area breakdowns)
- 4729.txt — Layout, Navigation, Header, Footer
- 8351.txt — Hero & Landing Page
- 2067.txt — Builder/Chat UI
- 5943.txt — Styling, Colors, Design System
- 1284.txt — Authentication & User Pages
- 7612.txt — Marketing & Content Pages
